233
00:13:25,159 --> 00:13:26,619
Charles. Elizabeth.

234
00:13:26,619 --> 00:13:27,656
Alice.

235
00:13:27,656 --> 00:13:29,888
Mereka adalah perabotku sayang.

236
00:13:29,888 --> 00:13:31,493
Oh.

237
00:13:31,493 --> 00:13:33,125
- Bagaimana dengan ini? - Apakah kamu gila?

238
